longBusinessSummary: Evolving Gold Corp., an exploration stage company, engages in the acquisition, exploration, and development of natural resource properties in Canada. The company explores for lithium deposit. Its flagship property is the Lithium Lakes property that covers an area of 72.5 square kilometers in Quebec. The company was formerly known as 6109527 Canada Ltd. and changed its name to Evolving Gold Corp. in September 2003. Evolving Gold Corp. was incorporated in 2003 and is headquartered in Vancouver, Canada.
